               THE BEST PLACES TO GOLF IN THE PACIFIC NORTHWEST & NORTHERN THAILAND! 
                Come join our  tour and golf at the most beautiful golf courses in the Pacific Northwestern United States and  Northern Thailand! 
               Ê 
             
             
               Ê 
               WE HAVE TWO TOURS FOR YOU TO CHOOSE FROM!  
                 
                Our Summer Golf Tour starts in June and ends in July / August. We will be enjoying the gloriously beautiful Golf Courses  
                of Washington, Idaho, and Montana, which lie within the Pacific Northwestern States of America.  
               Ê 
             
             
               Ê 
               Our Winter Golf Tour involves a total of 3 months at the magnificent Chiang-Mai Golf Course in Northern Thailand.  
               Ê 
             
             
               Ê 
               
			    Whether you choose the summer or winter tour for your golfing pleasure, you will enjoy the many  splendid resorts, spectacular golf courses, wonderful food, fun shopping and outstanding company!  
               Ê 
             
             
               Ê 
               ~~ This is a SPECIAL TEN-DAY TOUR PACKAGE that takes on approximately ten people per tour. ~~  
                The cost of the tour includes bus transportation, golfing fees, food, and hotel costs. Individuals of the group are  
                responsible for transportation to and from the airport, shopping, and casino visits. 
